snippet.title: TV Schedule | Cartoon Network Show Listings
snippet.description: Find a complete schedule of local listings for all your favorite shows. Discover what to watch and when to find it on Cartoon Network.

snippet.title: Pinocchio 2
snippet.description: Pinocchio learns that life as a real boy is harder than it looks. Watch more MAD on Cartoon Network!

snippet.title: It's Easter, Johnny Test!
snippet.description: Porkbelly's Annual Easter Egg Hunt is sabatoged by Dark Vegan when he turns the festivities into a hunt for Johnny Test!

snippet.title: Give Trees a Chance
snippet.description: Help Chowder make this a cleaner, greener planet for all of us. Plant a tree and make a difference!

snippet.title: Rump-A-Thump

snippet.title: Chowder
snippet.description: Chowder, under the instruction of Mung Daal, dreams of becoming a great chef someday. But the young apprentice must first find his way in the mystical city of Marzipan, where the simplest foods and recipes become the craziest adventures. Play free online games and watch video clips from Chowder on Cartoon Network.
